        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"DT Croatia vui mung khi lam nen lich su.\" title=\"\u0110T Croatia vui m\u1eebng khi l\u00e0m n\u00ean l\u1ecbch s\u1eed.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/16.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u0110T Croatia vui m\u1eebng khi l\u00e0m n\u00ean l\u1ecbch s\u1eed.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Croatia vs Anh:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-croatia-21-anh-421-190994.html\">3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Croatia 2-1 Anh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hlv-gareth-southgate-noi-sau-tran-thua-cua-dt-anh-465-190993.html\">HLV Gareth Southgate kh\u00f4ng d\u00e1m v\u00e0o ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3 sau tr\u1eadn thua c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hlv-croatia-ly-giai-nguyen-nhan-thang-anh-trong-tran-ban-ket-465-190992.html\">HLV Croatia l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i ngu\u1ed3n \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Anh trong tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ivan-perisic-vao-chung-ket-world-cup-ngo-nhu-mot-giac-mo-421-190991.html\">Ivan Perisic: V\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup ng\u1ee1 nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-huyen-thoai-bong-da-noi-gi-sau-tran-croatia-21-anh-421-190990.html\">Nh\u1eefng huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn Croatia 2-1 Anh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thong-ke-gay-soc-sau-that-bai-cua-anh-truoc-croatia-421-190989.html\">Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1152","checkdouble":"190995"},{"date":"06:30 12/07","title":"Harry Kane: \"Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia th\u1eadt \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/harry-kane-that-bai-truoc-croatia-that-dau-don.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Harry Kane ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Croatia vs Anh, ng\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng sau khi Tam s\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft nh\u01b0ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Tam s\u01b0 \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Harry Kane ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i v\u00ec Anh kh\u00f4ng v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Croatia \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, Anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 ngay t\u1eeb ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 5 do c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Kieran Trippier. Tuy nhi\u00ean, h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng th\u1eafng l\u1ea1i 2-1 sau 120 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Harry Kane ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Croatia vs Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Harry Kane ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Croatia vs Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/harry-kane-that-bai-truoc-croatia-that-dau-don.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Harry Kane ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Croatia vs Anh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-croatia-vs-anh-421-190986.html\" target=\"_blank\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Croatia vs Anh</span> gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc caro ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft g\u1eb7p Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0o Ch\u1ee7 nh\u1eadt tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, Anh ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u1ee1 h\u1eb9n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, 4 l\u1ea7n v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u1edf Euro v\u00e0 World Cup anh \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHarry Kane ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Croatia vs Anh, ng\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng sau khi Tam s\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\"\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c r\u1ea5t ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 v\u00e0 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng s\u1edbm. Sau \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi th\u00eam b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. N\u1ebfu Anh t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u1eafm ch\u1eafc chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cNgay c\u1ea3 khi h\u1ecd g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a Anh v\u1eabn ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u sao ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi th\u00eam b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u00e0y th\u1eadt cay \u0111\u1eafng, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng thua tr\u1eadn. T\u00f4i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Kane tin Anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00ec Anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, song ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Harry Kane v\u1eabn kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Tam s\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kane van chua co mot co hoi nao\" title=\"Kane v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0o\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/012424-kane.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kane tin Anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cAnh \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tr\u1ebb nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tham v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. NHM Anh c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cV\u1edbi d\u00e0n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, \u1edf Euro 2020 v\u00e0 World Cup 2022, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, khi \u0111\u00f3 Anh c\u00f2n \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3 h\u01a1n th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i. Khi \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i ni\u1ec1m tin n\u01a1i NHM, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-croatia-21-anh-421-190994.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-croatia-21-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-croatia-21-anh-421-190994.html\">3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Croatia 2-1 Anh</span><br>\r\nCroatia \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Anh 2-1 \u0111\u1ec3 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft g\u1eb7p Ph\u00e1p. C\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua danh s\u00e1ch 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau...</div>\r\n</div>\r\nAnh s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn tranh gi\u1ea3i 3 v\u1edbi B\u1ec9 trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Croatia trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u1edf World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1151","checkdouble":"190996"},{"date":"06:51 12/07","title":"Rashford kh\u00f3c h\u1ebft n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/rashford-khoc-het-nuoc-mat-sau-that-bai-cua-anh-truoc-croatia.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Marcus Rashford th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng sau tr\u1eadn thua 1-2 c\u1ee7a Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia, ng\u00f4i sao 20 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u sau khi Tam s\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nVi\u1ec7c Croatia t\u1ed1n qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ee9c l\u1ef1c trong hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0110an M\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 Nga gi\u00fap Anh chi\u1ebfm l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf l\u1edbn trong tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft 2 World Cup 2018. Tam s\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ngay sau ti\u1ebfng c\u00f2i khai cu\u1ed9c v\u00e0 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t s\u1edbm.<br />\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Marcus Rashford th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng sau tr\u1eadn thua 1-2 c\u1ee7a Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Marcus Rashford th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng sau tr\u1eadn thua 1-2 c\u1ee7a Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/Marcus-Rashford-that-vong-sau-tran-thua-1-2-cua-Anh-truoc-Croatia-hinh-anh.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u00a0\u0110T Anh th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nTrippier \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp hi\u1ec3m h\u00f3c \u0111\u01b0a Anh v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean t\u1eeb ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 5. Tuy nhi\u00ean, sau \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ee9c tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Tam s\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a Croatia. 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Perisic v\u00e0 Mandzukic gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc caro ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng th\u1eafng l\u1ea1i 2-1.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-croatia-vs-anh-421-190986.html\" target=\"_blank\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Croatia vs Anh </span>gi\u00fap Tam s\u01b0 l\u1ee1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, v\u1edbi b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh c\u00f9ng kinh nghi\u1ec7m, Croatia \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n v\u00e0o ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nTh\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Gareth Southgate r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng sau khi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft, nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1ecf ra bu\u1ed3n b\u00e3 sau tr\u1eadn thua Croatia 1-2.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Rashford kh\u00f3c nh\u01b0 m\u01b0a sau tr\u1eadn thua Croatia</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngay sau khi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i th\u1ed5i c\u00f2i k\u1ebft th\u00fac tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed5 g\u1ee5c xu\u1ed1ng s\u00e2n. Nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap h\u1ecd c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.\u00a0Nh\u1eefng gi\u1ecdt n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft \u0111\u00e3 r\u01a1i tr\u00ean khu\u00f4n m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Anh.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nMarcus Rashford th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng sau tr\u1eadn thua 1-2 c\u1ee7a Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia, ng\u00f4i sao 20 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u sau khi Tam s\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft, nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean trong BHL c\u1ee7a Anh \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfn t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1997.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<p>Nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u0111\u00e1ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Rashford sau tr\u1eadn thua Croatia.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Rashford roi nuoc mat ngay khi tran dau ket thuc\" title=\"Rashford r\u01a1i n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft ngay khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u k\u1ebft th\u00fac\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/064714-rashford.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Rashford r\u01a1i n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft ngay khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u k\u1ebft th\u00fac</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br />\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sau do do guc xuong san va tiep tuc khoc\" title=\"Sau \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed5 g\u1ee5c xu\u1ed1ng s\u00e2n v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c kh\u00f3c\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/do-guc.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sau \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed5 g\u1ee5c xu\u1ed1ng s\u00e2n v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c kh\u00f3c</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br />\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mac du duoc mot thanh vien trong BHL dong vien nhung cau thu 20 tuoi van rat buon\" title=\"M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean trong BHL \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 20 tu\u1ed5i v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t bu\u1ed3n\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/ngoi-day-khoc.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean trong BHL \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 20 tu\u1ed5i v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t bu\u1ed3n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br />\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Hinh anh dang thuong cua Pickford va Rashford\" title=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u0111\u00e1ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Pickford v\u00e0 Rashford\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/pic-va-rat.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u0111\u00e1ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Pickford v\u00e0 Rashford</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\u00a0</p>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1150","checkdouble":"190997"},{"date":"06:32 12/07","title":"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh tan m\u1ed9ng c\u00fap v\u00e0ng: Sau t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3, s\u1ee9c tr\u1ebb v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i ch\u00e0o thua kinh nghi\u1ec7m","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/nguoi-anh-tan-mong-cup-vang-sau-tat-ca-suc-tre-van-phai-chao-thua-kinh-nghiem.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u201cFootball is NOT coming home!\u201d \u2013 Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 mang b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 sau khi \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn trong th\u1ebf b\u1ecb Croatia l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng. Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn Croatia 2-1 Anh b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018?</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3, s\u1ee9c tr\u1ebb v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i ch\u00e0o thua kinh nghi\u1ec7m</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Anh b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u1edbi \u01b0u th\u1ebf trong \u0111\u1ea1i \u0111a s\u1ed1 c\u00e1c kh\u00eda c\u1ea1nh. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh s\u1ef1 nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n \u1edf ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh th\u00ec h\u1eefu h\u00ecnh h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng di\u1ec7n th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Trong khi Tam S\u01b0 ch\u1ec9 tr\u1ea3i qua 90 ph\u00fat t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ea3nh th\u01a1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u1edf tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, Croatia th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb tra t\u1ea5n th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 sau hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 240 ph\u00fat trong v\u00f2ng 5 ng\u00e0y v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n, \u0111\u00e1 hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5 r\u1ed3i s\u00fat lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u v\u1edbi c\u1ea3 \u0110an M\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m Anh vs Croatia Ng\u00e0y s\u1ee9c tr\u1ebb ch\u00e0o thua kinh nghi\u1ec7m h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m Anh vs Croatia Ng\u00e0y s\u1ee9c tr\u1ebb ch\u00e0o thua kinh nghi\u1ec7m h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/nguoi-anh-tan-mong-cup-vang-sau-tat-ca-suc-tre-van-phai-chao-thua-kinh-nghiem.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>D\u01b0 \u00e2m Anh vs Croatia: Ng\u00e0y s\u1ee9c tr\u1ebb ch\u00e0o thua kinh nghi\u1ec7m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">V\u00e0 \u0111\u1eebng qu\u00ean th\u00eam r\u1eb1ng, Anh s\u1edf h\u1eefu d\u00e0n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb trung v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i trung b\u00ecnh th\u1ea5p nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018, c\u00f2n th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 v\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a Croatia bao g\u1ed3m c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ea5p x\u1ec9 ho\u1eb7c ngo\u00e0i 30 \u2013 Modric, Rakitic, Mandzukic, Perisic, Subasic, Strinic, Lovren, Vida, Corluka, Pivaric, Badelj\u2026 <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">11 c\u00e1i t\u00ean n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ebfn 8 trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u.\u00a0<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i sao? Croatia th\u1eafng, trong th\u1ebf s\u1edbm b\u1ecb d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc ngay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 5 v\u00e0 b\u1ebf t\u1eafc su\u1ed1t h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3 sau \u0111\u00f3, v\u1edbi pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh trong hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5 th\u1ee9 hai, khi nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n bi\u1ebft \u0111i b\u1ed9 hay th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u0103n ra s\u00e2n \u00f4m ch\u00e2n \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">360 ph\u00fat t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng 4 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 quy chu\u1ea9n trong ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y m\u1ed9t tu\u1ea7n l\u1ec5, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-croatia-vs-anh-463-190974.html\" target=\"_blank\">Croatia th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00ea b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft g\u1eb7p Ph\u00e1p</span> \u1edf Moscow nh\u01b0ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n hi\u1ec3n vinh v\u00e0 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-croatia-vs-anh-461-190987.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Croatia 2-1 Anh (World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">R\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o, nh\u01b0ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n bi\u1ebft t\u1ef1 tr\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch v\u00ec sao r\u00f5 h\u01a1n cho lu\u1eadn \u0111i\u1ec3m b\u00ean tr\u00ean, Croatia th\u1eafng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u01b0ng d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 Anh c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ef1 thua, t\u1eeb tr\u00ean s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">S\u1ed1 ph\u1eadn tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft \u0111\u00e1ng l\u1ebd ra \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t ngay trong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi Kieran Trippier s\u1edbm khai th\u00f4ng th\u1ebf b\u1ebf t\u1eafc b\u1eb1ng c\u00fa s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft. Kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 Croatia l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh, Anh ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn r\u1ea5t ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 hi\u1ec3n nhi\u00ean t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng nguy hi\u1ec3m s\u1eafc n\u00e9t h\u01a1n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, vi\u1ec7c Harry Kane, trung phong xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t nh\u00ec th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u danh s\u00e1ch Vua Ph\u00e1 L\u01b0\u1edbi, kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong t\u01b0 th\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n nh\u01b0 m\u1ecdi khi, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng nh\u01b0 \u0111i\u1ec1m b\u00e1o l\u00e0nh \u00edt d\u1eef nhi\u1ec1u cho Tam S\u01b0 sau khi kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i 45 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u00e1ng ra ph\u1ea3i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng h\u01a1n n\u1eefa so v\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"an\" title=\"an\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-croatia-21-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>D\u01b0 \u00e2m Anh vs Croatia: Ng\u00e0y s\u1ee9c tr\u1ebb ch\u00e0o thua kinh nghi\u1ec7m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Y chang nh\u01b0 r\u1eb1ng ngay khi hi\u1ec7p hai khai cu\u1ed9c, Anh \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edbm c\u00f3 t\u01b0 t\u01b0\u1edfng b\u1ea3o to\u00e0n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 v\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ea7m ch\u1eebng h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n, k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 nh\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ea1i t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u1ea5t cho Croatia. Trong th\u1ebf b\u1ebf t\u1eafc, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n v\u00f9ng Balkan b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u01b0a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1ea1ch xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t, tr\u00fat g\u00e1nh n\u1eb7ng v\u00e0 \u1ee9c ch\u1ebf t\u00e2m l\u00fd sang nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p tr\u1ebb trung nh\u01b0ng non n\u1edbt kinh nghi\u1ec7m b\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tinh th\u1ea7n lung l\u1ea1c v\u00e0 tr\u1edf n\u00ean m\u1ea5t t\u1eadp trung, Anh ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1eaft kh\u00f4ng s\u1edbm th\u00ec mu\u1ed9n, trong khi Perisic tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng d\u00e2n t\u1ed9c b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch n\u00e0y hay c\u00e1ch kh\u00e1c. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-croatia-vs-anh-421-190986.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/ket-qua-croatia-vs-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-croatia-vs-anh-421-190986.html\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Croatia vs Anh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018</span><br>\r\nChuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt chi ti\u1ebft k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Croatia vs Anh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 h\u00f4m nay. Th\u00f4ng tin k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n, clip b\u00e0n th\u1eafng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Trong v\u00f2ng 4 ph\u00fat, ng\u00f4i sao Inter Milan su\u00fdt t\u1ef1 m\u00ecnh tr\u1eebng ph\u1ea1t Tam S\u01b0 l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 hai v\u1edbi c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u00e9o g\u00f3c d\u1ed9i c\u1ed9t d\u1ecdc, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i ch\u00ednh anh \u0111\u00e3 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o cho b\u00e0n th\u1eafng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a Mandzukic \u1edf hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5 th\u1ee9 hai, khi h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u00e1o tr\u1eafng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n l\u01a1 l\u00e0 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1ed5ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Juventus tho\u00e1t ra t\u1eeb \u0111\u1eb1ng sau l\u01b0ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn g\u00f3i g\u1ecdn trong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t, h\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 ai c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1eafc m\u1ea9m t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 chung k\u1ebft s\u1ebd thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ef1 tay trao n\u00f3 l\u1ea1i cho Croatia. M\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e1c \u0111i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u n\u1ebfu Harry Kane v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1eafc b\u00e9n, l\u1ea1nh l\u00f9ng h\u01a1n trong kh\u00e2u d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m, hay s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ec9nh t\u00e1o, b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ranh m\u00e3nh h\u01a1n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"O hiep phu thu hai, Mandzukic ghi ban an dinh chien thang giup Croatia lam nen lich su.\" title=\"\u1ede hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5 th\u1ee9 hai, Mandzukic ghi b\u00e0n \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng gi\u00fap Croatia l\u00e0m n\u00ean l\u1ecbch s\u1eed.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/061007-11.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>D\u01b0 \u00e2m Anh vs Croatia: Ng\u00e0y s\u1ee9c tr\u1ebb ch\u00e0o thua kinh nghi\u1ec7m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u00f3 \u00e2u c\u0169ng l\u00e0 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf c\u1ed1 h\u1eefu c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb khi ch\u1ec9 bi\u1ebft ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch ng\u00e2y th\u01a1 h\u1ed3n nhi\u00ean ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec3u x\u1ea3o c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 cho ph\u00e9p, \u0111\u01a1n c\u1eed nh\u01b0 g\u00e2y \u1ee9c ch\u1ebf t\u00e2m l\u00fd cho Croatia th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f2n \u0111ang d\u1eabn b\u00e0n v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00e2u c\u1ea3 th\u1eddi gian l\u1eabn th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">H\u00e3y nh\u00ecn Croatia trong 10 ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng khi h\u1ecd m\u1edbi l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u1edf g\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng h\u01a1n, nh\u00ecn xem Rakitic ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng to ti\u1ebfng khi\u00eau kh\u00edch Rashford, \u0111\u00e0n em k\u00e9m tu\u1ed5i anh c\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t th\u1eadp k\u1ef7, \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea5u hi\u1ec3u s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t gi\u1eefa s\u1ee9c tr\u1ebb v\u00e0 kinh nghi\u1ec7m.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi Gareth Southgate l\u1ed9 nguy\u00ean h\u00ecnh \u201ctay m\u01a1\u201d<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1ee9 nh\u1ea5t, HLV 47 tu\u1ed5i d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng r\u00fat ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc g\u00ec sau nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng nh\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn trong th\u1ebf d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c, Colombia kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tr\u1eebng ph\u1ea1t ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n, gi\u1edd th\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 Croatia \u2013 \u0111\u1ed9i th\u1ee9 2/18 sau Argentina n\u0103m 1990 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft b\u1ecb d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc sau 45 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Gareth Southgate noi sau tran thua cua DT Anh tai ban ket World Cup 2018.\" title=\"HLV Gareth Southgate n\u00f3i sau tr\u1eadn thua c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh t\u1ea1i b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/hlv-gareth-southgate-noi-sau-tran-thua-cua-dt-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>D\u01b0 \u00e2m Anh vs Croatia: HLV Gareth Southgate \u0111\u00e1ng t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t cho th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1ee9 hai v\u00e0 quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n, \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 linh ho\u1ea1t chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Ashley Young m\u1ea5t h\u00fat, Alli v\u00e0 Henderson ch\u00ecm ngh\u1ec9m \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa, Sterling nh\u1ea1t nh\u00f2a d\u1ea7n d\u00e0, Harry Kane b\u1ecb phong t\u1ecfa g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 di chuy\u1ec3n. Gareth Southgate \u00e1n binh b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng, ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng ngo\u00e1i nh\u00ecn b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho \u0111\u1ebfn hai hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3 ch\u00fat n\u00e0o.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Gi\u1ea3 nh\u01b0 \u00f4ng d\u0169ng c\u1ea3m v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111o\u00e1n h\u01a1n, Anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu k\u1ebft c\u1ee5c nghi\u1ec7t ng\u00e3 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. Tam S\u01b0 v\u1eabn x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng ng\u1ea9ng cao \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Southgate x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0 \u0111ang l\u00e0m, nh\u01b0ng r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u00f4ng v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i h\u1ecdc nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eafm v\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng c\u00e1i gi\u00e1 ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 qu\u00e1 \u0111\u1eaft ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay c\u0169ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 \u0111\u1ee7 cho nh\u1eefng kinh nghi\u1ec7m x\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e1u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Duy v\u1eadt hay duy t\u00e2m, c\u00fap v\u00e0ng c\u0169ng s\u1ebd kh\u1eafc t\u00ean ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">V\u1ed1n d\u0129 tr\u00ean l\u00fd thuy\u1ebft, Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao nh\u1ea5t \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018. Gi\u1edd khi \u0111\u00e3 an b\u00e0i k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, quan \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3 c\u00e0ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc h\u01a1n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ph\u00e1p kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i Anh, h\u1ecd v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 v\u00e0 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i \u0111a d\u1ea1ng chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Croatia ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c n\u1eb7ng g\u00e1nh b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c sau khi tr\u1ea3i qua th\u00eam 120 ph\u00fat n\u1eefa m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Ng\u1ed3i rung \u0111\u00f9i theo d\u00f5i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn \u1edf Moscow, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 r\u00fat ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ecdi b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc t\u1eeb ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e1ng gi\u1ec1ng b\u00ean kia eo bi\u1ec3n Manche \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 k\u1ebf s\u00e1ch \u1ee9ng ph\u00f3 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Phap vs Croatia chung ket World Cup 2018\" title=\"Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/062752-4.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018: V\u1edbi m\u1ecdi \u01b0u th\u1ebf trong tay, c\u00fap v\u00e0ng s\u1ebd l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 hai ghi danh Les Bleus?</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u01afu th\u1ebf th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e0nh, Ph\u00e1p c\u00f2n \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 b\u1edfi v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1\u2026 \u00e1o s\u1ed1ng. Nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y, Anh \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecf ngay khi t\u1eeb b\u1ecf b\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ecf s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi trang ph\u1ee5c truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia, v\u00e0 h\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 thua B\u1ec9 \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng khi m\u1eb7c \u00e1o tr\u1eafng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3 ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/croatia-thang-tien-o-world-cup-2018-hai-thap-ky-doi-cho-mot-the-he-vang-421-189353.html\" target=\"_blank\">th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 v\u00e0ng Croatia</span> tr\u00ean c\u1ea3 h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec1u di\u1ec7n b\u1ed9 s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch t\u00edm than cho d\u1ec5 ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng s\u1eafc \u0111\u1ecf ho\u1eb7c tr\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ea1n. Gi\u1edd trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng tranh c\u00fap v\u00e0ng, h\u1ecd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 trang ph\u1ee5c s\u1ecdc ca-r\u00f4 \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng khi Ph\u00e1p v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 \u01b0u ti\u00ean ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn b\u1ed9 \u00e1o lam truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Li\u1ec7u Croatia c\u0169ng s\u1ebd c\u1ea1n n\u1ed1t may m\u1eafn hay h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ph\u00e1 d\u1edbp b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n c\u1ed5 t\u00edch th\u1ea7n k\u1ef3 xuy\u00ean su\u1ed1t hai th\u1eadp k\u1ef7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh? Ai c\u0169ng hy v\u1ecdng, nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t v\u00e0o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p c\u0169ng sau hai th\u1eadp k\u1ef7 m\u00f2n m\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ee3i ch\u1edd. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 s\u1ebd h\u1ea1 m\u00e0n trong ng\u00e0y ch\u1ee7 nh\u1eadt 15/7 (22h00 gi\u1edd Vi\u1ec7t Nam).<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>D\u01b0 \u00e2m Anh vs Croatia b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018:</strong><strong><br>\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/nhung-hinh-anh-an-tuong-trong-ngay-dt-croatia-lam-nen-lich-su-465-190995.html\">Nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong ng\u00e0y \u0110T Croatia l\u00e0m n\u00ean l\u1ecbch s\u1eed</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/harry-kane-that-bai-truoc-croatia-that-dau-don-421-190996.html\">Harry Kane: Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia th\u1eadt \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/rashford-khoc-het-nuoc-mat-sau-that-bai-cua-anh-truoc-croatia-421-190997.html\">Rashford kh\u00f3c h\u1ebft n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hlv-gareth-southgate-noi-sau-tran-thua-cua-dt-anh-465-190993.html\">HLV Gareth Southgate kh\u00f4ng d\u00e1m v\u00e0o ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3 sau tr\u1eadn thua c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hlv-croatia-ly-giai-nguyen-nhan-thang-anh-trong-tran-ban-ket-465-190992.html\">HLV Croatia l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i ngu\u1ed3n \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Anh trong tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-huyen-thoai-bong-da-noi-gi-sau-tran-croatia-21-anh-421-190990.html\">Nh\u1eefng huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn Croatia 2-1 Anh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thong-ke-gay-soc-sau-that-bai-cua-anh-truoc-croatia-421-190989.html\">Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong> <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1149","checkdouble":"190998"},{"date":"06:41 12/07","title":"M\u1ea3i \u0103n m\u1eebng \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ed7i x\u00f4 ng\u00e3 ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean \u1ea3nh, Mandzukic \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ca ng\u1ee3i v\u00ec c\u00e1ch h\u00e0nh x\u1eed","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/12/mario-mandzukic-xo-nga-phong-vien-anh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1ea3i \u0103n m\u1eebng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng gi\u00fap Croatia v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft, Mario Mandzukic v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh x\u00f4 ng\u00e3 m\u1ed9t ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean \u1ea3nh v\u00e0 \u0110T Croatia sau \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e1ng y\u00eau.\r\nN.D (TTVN)\r\n</h2><div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-croatia-vs-anh-461-190987.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/clip-ban-thang-croatia-vs-anh.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-croatia-vs-anh-461-190987.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Croatia 2-1 Anh (World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 \u0111\u1ec3 thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5, song nh\u1edd c\u00e1c pha l\u00e0m b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Perisic v\u00e0 Mandzukic, Croatia \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c Anh v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1 \u0111\u1ec3 ghi t\u00ean m\u00ecnh v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mario Mandzukic x\u00f4 ng\u00e3 ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean \u1ea3nh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Mario Mandzukic x\u00f4 ng\u00e3 ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean \u1ea3nh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/Mario-Mandzukic-xo-nga-phong-vien-anh-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Mario Mandzukic \u0103n m\u1eebng cu\u1ed3ng nhi\u1ec7t sau b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho \u0110T Croatia.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mai \u0103n m\u1eebng \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ed7i x\u00f4 ng\u00e3 ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean \u1ea3nh, Mandzukic \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ca ng\u1ee3i v\u00ec c\u00e1ch h\u00e0nh x\u1eed h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 