18/3/6/thuc-hu-vu-psg-chi-100-trieu-euro-mua-kante.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>PSG mua Kante ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 tin \u0111\u1ed3n t\u1eeb ph\u00eda b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, Chelsea kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u01b0a nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ecfi mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">PSG \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n quan t\u00e2m Kante</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, PSG thi\u1ebfu \u0111i m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Thiago Motta \u0111\u00e3 36 tu\u1ed5i, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1982 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh trong c\u1ea3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ee5 PSG mua Kante v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ee5 PSG mua Kante v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/6/thuc-hu-vu-psg-chi-100-trieu-euro-mua-kante.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>PSG \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 quan t\u00e2m NGolo Kante c\u1ee7a Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf H\u00e8 2018. Nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/psg-chi-so-tien-sieu-khung-mua-sao-chelsea-172-188620.html\" target=\"_blank\">PSG quan t\u00e2m Kante</span> c\u1ee7a Chelsea, HLV Thomas Tuchel \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a anh v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n C\u00f4ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c Ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1eadm ch\u00ed The Sun c\u00f2n kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh PSG ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 100 tri\u1ec7u euro mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn tr\u1ea3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00ean t\u1edbi 12 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng/m\u00f9a. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 Paris \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u00f3 Kante b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 n\u1ec1n n\u1ea3ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c sung m\u00e3n c\u00f9ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111eo b\u00e1m d\u1ebbo dai.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKante c\u0169ng th\u00f4ng minh trong nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u00e1n \u0111o\u00e1n, c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c anh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a PSG s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn PSG ch\u01b0a h\u1ecfi mua Kante</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">PSG mua Kante ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 tin \u0111\u1ed3n t\u1eeb ph\u00eda b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, Chelsea kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u01b0a nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ecfi mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kante duoc cham diem cao nhat tran Leicester vs Chelsea\" title=\"Kante \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ea5m \u0111i\u1ec3m cao nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn Leicester vs Chelsea\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/19/Real,-Barca-va-PSG-muon-dua-tien-ve-Kante-roi-Chelsea-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u01b0a nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb n\u00e0o cho Kante\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn ch\u01b0a nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb n\u00e0o d\u00e0nh cho Kante, v\u00e0 n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o h\u1ecfi mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i h\u1ecd c\u0169ng ki\u00ean quy\u1ebft t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i. Chelsea kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Kante l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf v\u00e0 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Maurizio Sarri \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 s\u1eafp thay Antonio Conte d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Chelsea, \u00f4ng n\u00e0y mu\u1ed1n The Blues gi\u1eef Kante \u1edf l\u1ea1i. B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u00ecnh y\u00eau v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Kante r\u1eddi Chelsea \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed anh c\u00f2n \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1146","checkdouble":"190952"},{"date":"16:03 11/07","title":"Everton \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua h\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i Barca v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 24 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/everton-dat-duoc-thoa-thuan-mua-hang-thai-barca-voi-gia-24-trieu-bang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>B\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n song Croatia v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u1edf tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft gi\u1eefa \u0110T Anh vs Croatia n\u1ebfu th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga theo c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ea7y kh\u00f3 nh\u1ecdc \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, \u0110T Croatia \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u00e0 \u0110T Anh.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1edf h\u1eefu nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00f4i sao c\u00f9ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng c\u1ef1c k\u00ec l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i, \u0111\u00e2y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c v\u1edbi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Zlatko Dalic, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u1ebfu v\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.</p>\r\n<h2>1. Ra s\u00e2n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh 4-1-4-1</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Marcelo Brozovic \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T Nga. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao \u1edf n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c, t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u00e1nh ch\u1eb7n, Brozovic \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1n gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 mang \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft cho h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7 Croatia.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00ec th\u1ebf Croatia n\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ea5p nh\u1ea5t trong tuy\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 5 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh. \u0110\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch gi\u00fap h\u1ecd ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba t\u1eeb xa nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00ean b\u00f3ng nguy hi\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Tam s\u01b0.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"4 vi\u1ec7c Croatia c\u1ea7n l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0110T Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"4 vi\u1ec7c Croatia c\u1ea7n l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0110T Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/4-viec-Croatia-can-lam-de-danh-bai-DT-Anh-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110T Croatia n\u00ean c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 tr\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba t\u1eeb xa nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ee3t t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Anh</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e1 tr\u00ean Brozovic s\u1ebd l\u00e0 b\u1ed9 t\u1ee9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Modric, Rebic, Perisic Rakitic c\u00f2n Mario Mandzukic l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o duy nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. Ngo\u00e0i ra, Mateo Kovacic c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ebf ch\u1ed7 Brozovic. Ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Real Madrid kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nhi\u1ec1u \u1edf gi\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y v\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn anh s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.</p>\r\n<h2>2. Ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t khu trung tuy\u1ebfn</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Croatia bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n th\u1eafng trong vi\u1ec7c ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t khu trung tuy\u1ebfn m\u1edbi m\u01a1 c\u00f3 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi. HLV Southgate l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111ang s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng hai ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00f3 xu h\u01b0\u1edbng ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u1edf trung t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 l\u00e0 Dele Alli v\u00e0 Jesse Lingaard. V\u00e0 h\u1ecd th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 thi\u00ean h\u01b0\u1edbng ch\u01a1i d\u00e2ng cao \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng HLV Zlatko Dalic n\u00ean khai th\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o \u00e1p l\u1ef1c v\u1edbi Jordan Henderson, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111ang n\u1eafm gi\u1eef tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t \u0110T Anh s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, Croatia ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t nh\u1ecbp \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. V\u00ec th\u1ebf h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c ch\u1eadm r\u00e3i, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn v\u00e0 ch\u1edd th\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec3 tung ra nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f2n ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 k\u1ebft li\u1ec5u \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.</p>\r\n<h2>3. Khai th\u00e1c kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng sau l\u01b0ng c\u00e1c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00ean b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111ang ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i Kieran Trippier. V\u00ec th\u1ebf c\u00e1c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Croatia c\u1ea7n khai th\u00e1c kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng m\u00e0 c\u00e1c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0110T Anh \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nh\u1eb1m t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ivan Rakitic c\u00f3 xu hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e1 b\u00f3 v\u00e0o trong nh\u01b0ng Perisic th\u00ec ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 g\u00e2y \u00e1p l\u1ef1c b\u00ean h\u00e0nh lang c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c trung v\u1ec7 Anh m\u1ea5t \u0111i s\u1ef1 t\u1eadp trung, t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho Mandzukic v\u00e0 Rebic c\u00f3 kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m. Rebic c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 t\u1ea7m ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng r\u1ea5t r\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Croatia c\u00f3 th\u00eam nhi\u1ec1u ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Trippier\" title=\"Trippier\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/bai-du-thi-an-tuong-world-cup-16-nam-mot-tinh-yeu-nguyen-ven.jpg\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Croatia c\u1ea7n t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1t c\u00e1c kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng sau l\u01b0ng Trippier</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>4. Luy\u1ec7n c\u00e1ch ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n c\u00e1c t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng 'b\u1eadc th\u1ea7y' v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh. V\u00e0 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Croatia c\u1ea7n nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9 s\u1ef1 nguy hi\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n thua t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua c\u1ea3 Colombia l\u1eabn Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n c\u0169ng t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1edbp th\u1eddi c\u01a1 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0 Harry Maguire, Harry Kane v\u00e0 John Stones. Ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1ea1t c\u00e1nh hay chuy\u1ec1n b\u1ed5ng c\u1ee7a Young hay Trippier, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mang v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Do v\u1eady, h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Croatia s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u1ec9nh t\u00e1o v\u00e0 kh\u00f4n ngoan \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ghi b\u00e0n.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-croatia-vs-anh-1h00-ngay-127-ve-nha-duoc-khong-bong-da-421-190906.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/nhan-dinh-croatia-vs-anh-1h00-ngay-127-ve-nha-duoc-khong-bong-da.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-croatia-vs-anh-1h00-ngay-127-ve-nha-duoc-khong-bong-da-421-190906.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Croatia vs Anh (1h00 ng\u00e0y 12/7): V\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00f4ng, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1?</span><br>\r\n28 n\u0103m l\u1ebb m\u1ed9t tu\u1ea7n, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee3i ch\u1edd \u0111\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1eb5ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady cho ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay &ndash; B\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup, m\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n h\u01a1n t\u1edbi c\u00fap v\u00e0ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, m\u1ed9t Croatia...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/jesse-lingard-can-gi-qua-bong-de-tao-nen-su-khac-biet-421-190941.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/jesse-lingard-can-gi-qua-bong-de-tao-nen-su-khac-biet.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/jesse-lingard-can-gi-qua-bong-de-tao-nen-su-khac-biet-421-190941.html\">Jesse Lingard: C\u1ea7n g\u00ec qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t?</span><br>\r\nB\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, Anh vs Croatia v\u1edbi tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i tr\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y. Nh\u1eefng b\u1eadc th\u1ea7y Modric v\u00e0 Rakitic th\u1eeba s\u1ee9c l\u00e0m n\u00ean s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi b\u00f3ng trong ch\u00e2n,...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/day-nguyen-nhan-croatia-vao-ban-ket-world-cup-2018-421-190863.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/day-nguyen-nhan-croatia-vao-ban-ket-world-cup-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/day-nguyen-nhan-croatia-vao-ban-ket-world-cup-2018-421-190863.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n Croatia v\u00e0o t\u1edbi b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup</span><br>\r\nCroatia v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 g\u1eb7p \u0110T Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ef1 s\u1eedng s\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi. \u0110\u1ebfn c\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Filip Tapalovic c\u0169ng ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y, nh\u01b0ng \u00f4ng kh\u1eb3ng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1145","checkdouble":"190953"},{"date":"15:53 11/07","title":"\u201cSi\u00eau \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng\u201d Croatia x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e0nh Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/bong-dung-mat-thuong-hieu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Davor Suker ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Modric tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Croatia vs Anh. Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Croatia kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110TQG x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e0nh Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Suker ca ng\u1ee3i Modric</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLuka Modric \u0111ang tr\u1ea3i qua nh\u1eefng th\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p. Anh \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng gi\u00fap Real Madrid gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League m\u00f9a th\u1ee9 3 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp. T\u1edbi World Cup 2018, Modric ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c mang theo phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 32 tu\u1ed5i hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i hay nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1ea3i v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a Croatia t\u1edbi b\u00e1n k\u1ebft c\u00fap th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb n\u0103m 1998. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Anh t\u1ea1i Moscow, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Croatia, Davor Suker \u2013 m\u1ed9t c\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00edch th\u1ee9 3 t\u1ea1i World Cup c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 20 n\u0103m \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh l\u1eddi ca ng\u1ee3i Modric.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Suker ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Modric tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Croatia vs Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Suker ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Modric tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Croatia vs Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/bong-dung-mat-thuong-hieu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Suker ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Modric v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHuy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Croatia tin r\u1eb1ng h\u1eadu b\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 th\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9c t\u00f4n 10 n\u0103m th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo v\u00e0 Lionel Messi. \u201c\u0110\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trong ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3\u201d, Suker ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Modric tr\u00ean ESPN.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cModric l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t h\u00ecnh m\u1eabu c\u1ea3 trong v\u00e0 ngo\u00e0i s\u00e2n cho t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ee9a tr\u1ebb, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u1edf Croatia. N\u1ebfu t\u00f4i c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t l\u00e1 phi\u1ebfu trong cu\u1ed9c b\u1ea7u ch\u1ecdn Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd b\u1ea7u cho c\u1eadu \u1ea5y.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>M\u01a1 v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u00f9 \u0110T Croatia \u0111\u1ee5ng ph\u1ea3i Anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, Suker v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7y l\u1ea1c quan. \u00d4ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng cho m\u1ed9t t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u01b0\u01a1i s\u00e1ng b\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Modric va dong doi Croatia\" title=\"Modric va dong doi Croatia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/Mandzukic-phat-bieu-ve-Modric,-dong-doi-tai-DT-Croatia-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Croatia v\u00e0o t\u1edbi b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i r\u1ea5t b\u00ecnh th\u1ea3n tr\u00ean kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i b\u1edfi t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 ranh gi\u1edbi mong manh gi\u1eefa chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i\u201d, c\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 50 tu\u1ed5i n\u00f3i th\u00eam. \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i b\u1edfi \u0110an M\u1ea1ch v\u00e0o 16 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc. T\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u1edf b\u00ean b\u1ed1 m\u1eb9, \u0103n u\u1ed1ng v\u00e0 xem World Cup tr\u00ean TV.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n Croatia \u0111\u1ed5 ra \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng. B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u00e0 th\u1ee9 r\u1ea5t thi\u00eang li\u00eang. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng cho ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0o n\u0103m 1998 v\u00e0 gi\u1edd x\u00e2y ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea7ng 2 c\u1ee7a n\u00f3.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 \u0110T Croatia tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dt-anh-nhan-tin-vui-truoc-tran-dai-chien-croatia-421-190921.html\">\u0110T Anh nh\u1eadn tin vui tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn Croatia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/an-tuong-world-cup/croatia-tu-davor-suker-den-luca-mondric-471-190912.html\">B\u00e0i d\u1ef1 thi \u1ea4n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng World Cup: Croatia - T\u1eeb Davor Suker \u0111\u1ebfn Luka Modric</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-croatia-vs-anh-1h00-ngay-127-ve-nha-duoc-khong-bong-da-421-190906.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Croatia vs Anh (1h00 ng\u00e0y 12/7): V\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00f4ng, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/rakitic-va-modric-se-giup-croatia-danh-bai-anh-421-190875.html\">Rakitic v\u00e0 Modric s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Croatia \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Anh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/day-nguyen-nhan-croatia-vao-ban-ket-world-cup-2018-421-190863.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n Croatia v\u00e0o t\u1edbi b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1144","checkdouble":"190955"},{"date":"16:32 11/07","title":"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n l\u00f9n nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi khen ng\u1ee3i Pickford","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/4/campos-phat-bieu-ve-pickford-thu-mon-tuyen-anh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Jorge Campos ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Pickford, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n b\u1ecb xem th\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1edfi chi\u1ec1u cao khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n. Campos c\u0169ng t\u1eebng tr\u1ea3i qua t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 v\u00e0 b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 th\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m cho h\u1eadu b\u1ed1i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Pickford b\u1ecb Courtois ch\u1ebf nh\u1ea1o</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nJordan Pickford \u0111ang c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t cao t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. Nh\u1eefng pha c\u1ee9u thua xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf Everton tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u1ebft Colombia r\u1ed3i Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap \u0110T Anh l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1edbi b\u00e1n k\u1ebft gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u, Pickford nh\u1eadn ph\u1ea3i nhi\u1ec1u nghi ng\u1edd khi c\u00f2n tr\u1ebb v\u00e0 m\u1edbi c\u00f3 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n 24 tu\u1ed5i c\u00e0ng ch\u01a1i c\u00e0ng hay v\u00e0 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ef1a \u0111\u00e1ng tin c\u1eady c\u1ee7a Anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Campos ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Pickford, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111ang b\u1ecb xem th\u01b0\u1eddng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Campos ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Pickford, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111ang b\u1ecb xem th\u01b0\u1eddng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/campos-phat-bieu-ve-pickford-thu-mon-tuyen-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Pickford b\u1ecb ch\u1ebf nh\u1ea1o v\u1ec1 chi\u1ec1u cao</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, Pickford t\u1eebng b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p Thibaut Courtois ch\u1ebf gi\u1ec5u v\u1ec1 chi\u1ec1u cao khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n ch\u1ec9 1m85 sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-1 c\u1ee7a Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9 cu\u1ed1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. V\u1ec1 ph\u1ea7n m\u00ecnh, tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 x\u1ee9 s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u ti\u1ebfng v\u00e0 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eefng nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t tr\u00ean \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1edbi m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Campos b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 th\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nJorge Campos l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi hi\u1ec3u h\u01a1n ai h\u1ebft t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng m\u00e0 Pickford \u0111ang tr\u1ea3i qua. Anh l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u00f3 ti\u1ebfng v\u1edbi 130 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n cho \u0110T Mexico, c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf 2 k\u1ef3 World Cup 1994 v\u00e0 1998. B\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta nh\u1eafc nhi\u1ec1u t\u1edbi Campos b\u1edfi chi\u1ec1u cao ch\u1ec9 1m70, r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5p trong l\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"thu mon Jorge Campos\" title=\"thu mon Jorge Campos\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/thu-mon-Jorge-Campos.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Campos ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Pickford v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u1ea3m th\u00f4ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Campos ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Pickford v\u00e0 d\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen cho h\u1eadu b\u1ed1i. \u201c\u0110ang c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 Jordan Pickford\u201d, c\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Mexico n\u00f3i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean. \u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 pha c\u1ee9u thua hi\u1ebfm c\u00f3 v\u00e0 th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cM\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 xem tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa B\u1ec9 v\u00e0 Brazil, n\u01a1i th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Thibaut Courtois \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u pha c\u1ee9u thua \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i. Ngo\u00e0i ra, Hugo Lloris c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p c\u0169ng \u0111ang l\u00e0m r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 World Cup 2018 tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/jesse-lingard-can-gi-qua-bong-de-tao-nen-su-khac-biet-421-190941.html\">Jesse Lingard: C\u1ea7n g\u00ec qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/phap-10-bi-ty-so-rat-nho-cach-biet-rat-lon-421-190914.html\">Ph\u00e1p 1-0 B\u1ec9: T\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 r\u1ea5t nh\u1ecf, c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-phap-10-bi-mot-thoi-thuong-cua-bong-da-the-gioi-la-day-421-190903.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Ph\u00e1p 1-0 B\u1ec9: M\u1ed1t th\u1eddi th\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/diem-nhan-phap-vs-bi-tran-cau-thuc-dung-421-190893.html\">5 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng si\u00eau th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1143","checkdouble":"190958"}]}